          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2116.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces and add them to a baking tray with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2116.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2116.-step-5-x400.jpg",
