          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2116.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>cheesy pepperoni free range chicken</strong> from the dish and give the <strong>tomato sauce</strong> a good mix up</p><p>Serve the <strong>cheesy pepperoni free range chicken</strong> over the<strong> tomato sauce</strong> with the <strong>crispy potatoes</strong> and<strong> salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
